OL,3,CMan who attacked lone women at
OL,4,Cknifepoint found guilty of rape
OL,6,FA 'sexual predator' who raped lone
OL,7,Fwomen at knifepoint in Manchester city
OL,8,Fcentre has been found guilty of three
OL,9,Fcounts of rape.
OL,11,FStuart Thomson, 34, attacked his
OL,12,Fvictims on Mancunian Way in the early
OL,13,Fhours on 31st January.
OL,15,FGreater Manchester Police received
OL,16,Fthree separate reports of rape, as
OL,17,Fwell as one of attempted rape, all
OL,18,Ffrom the same location on the same
OL,19,Fnight.
