OL,6,FA manhunt was launched, with
OL,7,Fdetectives trawling CCTV, where
OL,8,FThomson was seen wearing a distinctive
OL,9,Foutfit.
OL,11,FAt the scene, police also recovered a
OL,12,Fwool hat, which was mentioned in one
OL,13,Fof the victim statements. It was
OL,14,Fseized for forensics, but initially
OL,15,Fcame back matching someone who did not
OL,16,Fmatch Thomson's description.
