OL,6,FHowever, when detectives went to his
OL,7,Faddress, which was a hostel, to
OL,8,Fconduct enquiries, they spotted
OL,9,FThomson wearing a distinctive green
OL,10,Fjacket that had been identified during
OL,11,Fthe CCTV trawls.
OL,13,FAfter pleading not guilty, on 28
OL,14,FNovember, a jury found Thomson of
OL,15,FBuxton Road, Stockport, guilty of
OL,16,Fthree counts of rape, attempted rape,
OL,17,Fsexual assault, three counts of
OL,18,Fthreatening another with a bladed
OL,19,Farticle, and possession of a bladed
OL,20,Farticle following a ten-day trial at
OL,21,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
