OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Jennifer Savazzi
OL,7,Ffrom Greater Manchester Police said:
OL,8,F"It's clear that Stuart Thomson is a
OL,9,Fdangerous sexual predator. He forcibly
OL,10,Fimposed himself upon these women in a
OL,11,Fviolent and callous way with no
OL,12,Fconsideration for the damage he was
OL,13,Fdoing to them.
