OL,6,F"I would like to praise our victims
OL,7,Fand survivors who have shown
OL,8,Fextraordinary courage throughout and
OL,9,Fhave done all they can to assist the
OL,10,Finvestigation and prosecution, it is
OL,11,Ftheir courage which has got us here
OL,12,Ftoday. This has been a lengthy and
OL,13,Fdifficult process for them, and I am
OL,14,Ffull of admiration for the courage and
OL,15,Ftenacity they have shown.
