OL,6,F"By not accepting responsibility,
OL,7,FThompson has forced them to relive
OL,8,Ftheir pain throughout this trial. The
OL,9,Fharm offenders like Thomson cause are
OL,10,Fincalculable, but I hope this prison
OL,11,Fsentence goes some way in reassuring
OL,12,Four victims, survivors, and members of
OL,13,Fthe public that a dangerous man is off
OL,14,Four streets."
OL,16,FThomson is due to be sentenced in
OL,17,FJanuary 2025.
